{"tid":1055026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：警隊有柔情、溫馨、媽媽一面","createTime":"2019-03-10T09:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T11:08:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfa2bef14690f94d07afddbfa07ab37c6314a56","tid":1055026,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190310/s00001/043749260af48eec119a8cb1db7f1230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190310%2Fs00001%2F043749260af48eec119a8cb1db7f1230.jpg&h=0bc02a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司長張建宗出席監警會活動，其間談及警隊女警比例高，形容警隊「有媽媽的一面」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗發言時，提到監警會主席梁定邦說「我們警隊像綿羊般，他們有溫柔、溫馨的一面」，而他補充：「警隊有5000多名女警，佔警隊人數差不多五分之一，督察級佔三分之一，警司級是四分之一，所以我們（警隊）有柔情的一面，有溫馨的一面，有媽媽的一面。」<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又稱，警隊過去十年面對不少挑戰，憑着他們優秀的表現、專業精神和高質素訓練，成功闖過每個難關：「在香港我們每天上班下班都很安全，晚上出去不用擔心。為什麼我們不會擔心？就是因為我們有一隊極高效、優良和可靠的警隊。」<br />\n<br />\n張建宗另形容監警會是「正直不柯、不偏不倚、公平公正、透明度高」的組織，對其努力予以欣賞和高度肯定。"},{"pid":"c652e5a464a29988ea43a284710106057e63f950","tid":1055026,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190310/s00001/1552208299899/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190310%2Fs00001%2F1552208299899%2F&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=cd2c806d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190310%2Fs00001%2F1552208299899%2F&h=d98c4927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190310/s00001/1552208299899/</a>"},{"pid":"a2bdb908f44c3e681056294ab974f635e17cffb8","tid":1055026,"uid":117422,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"慈母手中棍"},{"pid":"9e80b6c40c02559b59a1bbb217724099aeb8a863","tid":1055026,"uid":191352,"like":3,"d